successes.title: Wrath of Kings
successes.description: An epic fantasy miniatures war game set in a stunning world. Beautiful miniatures, great art and fast rules!

Pledges.description: A la Carte - This is the level to pick if you just want to buy from the optional items menu.
Commander - One Faction Starter of your choice (MSRP $60)
King (early bird) -  Faction Starters of your choice, one exclusive* variant cover hardback rulebook, and one exclusive* "Iron Eyes" variant miniature. (MSRP $160)
King - 2 Faction Starters of your choice, one exclusive* variant cover hardback rulebook, and one exclusive* "Iron Eyes" variant miniature. (MSRP $160)
Ancient King (early bird) - All 5 Faction Starters, one exclusive* variant cover hardback rulebook, and one exclusive* "Iron Eyes" variant miniature. (MSRP $280)
